        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;b&gt;Smarter Pretrial Detention for Drug Charges Act of 2023&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill removes the presumption of pretrial detention for an individual who is charged with a federal drug offense for which the maximum term of imprisonment is 10 years or more.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
